  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK590">
<l>ciṟappaṟiya voṟṟiṉkaṭ ceyyaṟka ceyyiṟ </l>
<l> puṟappaṭuttā ṉāku maṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let not a king publicly confer on a spy any marks of his favour; if he does, he will divulge his own secret.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
